<subSubSection pageId="107" pageNumber="385" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="107.[1404,2610,1285,1984]" pageId="107" pageNumber="385">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1406,1752,1837,1866]" pageId="107" pageNumber="385">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Given the restricted distribution of the Talamancan Deermouse, it should be carefully monitored.
</paragraph>
